						<summary>

						<p>Fragment lying near the village Chāvadi.</p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara: Sadāśivadēva.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary epigraph mentions only the <hi rend="bold">Śaka year 1469.</hi> It corresponds to 1547 A.D.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. It registers the gift of the village Koṇḍa-samudram, inclusive of all privileges, as an <hi rend="italic">agrahāra</hi> by Rāmarāju Venkatādri Ayadēva-Mahārāju.</p>						

						</summary>
